title: Recap: Tech picks up two shutout wins Saturday - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech picks up two shutout wins Saturday - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The Red Raider softball team came away with a pair of two-hit shutouts on day two of the Jeannine McHaney Memorial Classic. Texas Tech (7-11) defeated North Texas (9-3) by a score of 3-0 and Southern (2-14) by a score of 5-0 Saturday at Rocky Johnson Field.
